name: South Dakota Secretary of State
tweet: The Secretary of State's office validated petitions today for a ballot measure that will appear on the General Election ballot in November.  The measure will be titled Constitutional Amendment D.  Further information on the 2022 Ballot Questions may be found on the SOS website.
